<item>
            <title>[LU-14797] lfs setquota should be nodemap aware</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14797</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When nodemap is used in conjunction with project quota to restrict clients to a given fileset, it should not be possible to alter other project quotas with &lt;tt&gt;lfs setquota&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
